aspectRatio.name: aspectRatio
aspectRatio.tooltip: The model defaults to matching the output image size to that of your input image, or otherwise generates 1:1 squares. You can control the aspect ratio of the output image using the aspect ratio

imageSize.name: imageSize
imageSize.tooltip: Control the resolution of the output image. 1K is approximately 1024x1024, 2K is approximately 2048x2048, 4K is approximately 4096x4096 (Only effective for the gemini-3 model).

enableSearch.name: enableSearch
enableSearch.tooltip: Use the Google Search tool to generate images based on real-time information (Only effective for the gemini-3 model)
